reviewText: This is the most enjoyable video I've seen in ages. Whenever my mood starts to darken, I'll watch this video and it just makes me happy. The song itself has to be rated one of the best children's song of the century, and the video captures the innocent joy and affirmation of pure love that the song invokes. This video is the best bargain on Amazon. It isn't everyday that you can find something that just makes you want to rejoice that you're alive in this world.
